  "title": "Production Quality Control Supervisor",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p>Grow with our food manufacturing division,\nsupporting the production of ready to eat meals supplied to retail, catering\nand vending channels.</p><p>Actual work involves monitoring production\nquality, hygiene standards and product consistency.</p><p>You can expect to be:</p><p>1. Conducting quality checks at each production\nstage.</p><p>2. Maintaining food safety and traceability\nrecords.</p><p>3. Training production staff on hygiene and\nSOPs.</p><p>4. Investigating quality issues and\nimplementing corrective actions.</p><p>5. Supporting audits and certification\nrequirements.</p><p>All local candidates with a keen interest for\nfood and is enthusiastic to join a growing local food company are invited to\napply. This role is primarily factory based and may require shift work.</p>",
