    "description": "<p>   Saybons is a casual French cafe chain with catering facilities, known for their media acclaimed French soups served in a cup and delicious savoury and sweet crepes. With a mission to make good French food accessible to everyone, Saybons offers not just a cafe experience in their retail outlets, but also full catering services, breakfast catering, live crepe stations and egg stations, as well as drop off buffet menus and French lunch boxes for both private and corporate sessions. Visit Saybons, or let the Saybons chef bring an unique and affordable French dining experience to you!</p>  <p>   Saybons is the retail brand name created and wholly owned by French Food Factory Pte Ltd.</p>  ",
